To use eclipse CDT, please follow these steps:

install eclipse & CDT plugin for C/C++
$ sudo apt-get install eclipse eclipse-cdt g++

install opencv and verify the installation path
/usr/local/include/opencv
/usr/local/include/opencv2

open eclipse and select the following workspace
<your_root_dir>/AOD_System/proj/Eclipse_Projects
and the suite of eclipse projects will open


To build the required libraries
bgs->
$ cd <your_root_dir>/AOD_System/lib/bgslibrary/build
$ cmake ..
$ make
be sure that file "libbgs.a" is generated

pd->
$ cd <your_root_dir>/AOD_System/lib/pdlibrary/build
$ cmake ..
$ make
be sure that file "libpd.a" is generated
